latestPosts.caption:
Time to grwm again 🩷 

Today’s look: 
Top: @nonaoofficial 
Jeans: @topshop 
Jewellery: @opulence_dxb (told you it’s become my favourite pair) 
Shoes: @louisvuitton 
Makeup staples from @toofacedlovesindia @toofaced 
Sunglasses: bought them from some random store in Croatia
Bag: again, from some store in Rome I don’t remember

You know that feeling when your outfit just clicks—it’s beautiful, comfortable, and makes you feel like the best version of yourself? That’s exactly how I felt in this @urthlabel look last night. I love the color, the silhouette, the comfort—just everything about it. I kept it minimal and accessorised with my current favorite earrings and handcuff from @opulence_dxb (disclaimer: you’ll be seeing me style these with a lot of my looks - they are dainty and easy and stunning!)

Grwm for an easy dinner party ❣️ 

Outfit: @houseofaurea_
